  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This post-marketing surveillance (PMS) is conducted to collect safety and efficacy data among
      subjects with chronic hepatitis B and hepatic cirrhosis B who is treated with adefovir
      tablets.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
